OL,3,CThe dads of two Southport attack
OL,4,Cvictims finish London marathon together
OL,6,FThe fathers of two of the girls killed
OL,7,Fin the Southport attack have crossed
OL,8,Fthe finish line of the London marathon
OL,9,Ftogether.
OL,11,FDavid Stancombe and Sergio Aguiar were
OL,12,Famong more than 60,000 people to
OL,13,Ftackle the race and completed the
OL,14,Fcourse in a time of four hours and 36
OL,15,Fminutes.
OL,17,FThe men's daughters, Elsie Dot
OL,18,FStancombe, seven, and Alice da Silva
OL,19,FAguiar, nine, were murdered in the
OL,20,FSouthport mass stabbing in July 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
