PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777374175
OL,3,CThe dads of two Southport attack
OL,4,Cvictims finish London marathon together
OL,6,FAfter completing the 26.2-mile course
OL,7,Flast year to raise money for projects
OL,8,Fset up in memory of their daughters,
OL,9,FMr Stancombe and Mr Aguiar returned to
OL,10,Frace side by side again in this years
OL,11,Fevent.
OL,13,FAhead of the race, they were presented
OL,14,Fwith Spirit of London Marathon Awards,
OL,15,Fdesigned to celebrate the "unique
OL,16,Fspirit" of the event and highlight
OL,17,Fparticipants' stories. The awards
OL,18,Fgrant them a spot at the event for
OL,19,Flife.
OL,26,@wD@[OUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777374175
OL,3,CThe dads of two Southport attack
OL,4,Cvictims finish London marathon together
OL,6,FMr Stancombe said he is "very proud"
OL,7,Fto have received the award, adding
OL,8,Fthat he is pleased to see schools
OL,9,Fmaking it a "personal mission" to
OL,10,Fencourage children to run since he and
OL,11,FMr Aguiar took on the marathon last
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,FHe added that he was pleased to see
OL,15,Fsome of Elsie's friends race in the
OL,16,FTCS Mini Marathon in the capital on
OL,17,FSaturday.
OL,26,@nD@YOUnD@dO]qD@MOUqD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777374175
OL,3,CThe dads of two Southport attack
OL,4,Cvictims finish London marathon together
OL,6,F"Seeing Elsie's friends run and know
OL,7,Fthey have been on a journey to get
OL,8,Fhere makes it very special. Taking
OL,9,Fpart in the TCS Mini London Marathon
OL,10,Fis the result of those efforts and I
OL,11,Freally hope they enjoy it as much as I
OL,12,Fwill," Mr Stancombe said.
OL,14,FElsie's Story, the charity Mr
OL,15,FStancombe raced for on Sunday, which
OL,16,Fwas founded in her memory, provides
OL,17,Fmedical care and bereavement support
OL,18,Fto children and families, as well as
OL,19,Forganising community events.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
