FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777374175
OL,3,CThe dads of two Southport attack
OL,4,Cvictims finish London marathon together
OL,6,FMr Aguiar said he "couldn't believe"
OL,7,Fhe had received the award, adding that
OL,8,Fhe runs for his daughter Alice, to
OL,9,F"spread her magic".
OL,11,FHe said: "I spoke to my wife and I
OL,12,Fjust said, 'wow'. I run for my
OL,13,Fdaughter to take her legacy and spread
OL,14,Fher magic and when I received this, I
OL,15,Fcouldn't believe it. It means a lot
OL,16,Fand it is a gift from my princess for
OL,17,Fus.
OL,26,@nD@SOUnD@dO]qD@AOUqD@RO]sD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777374175
OL,3,CThe dads of two Southport attack
OL,4,Cvictims finish London marathon together
OL,6,F"It is very emotional being here but
OL,7,Fthese are inspirational children and I
OL,8,Ffeel proud that we can be here as part
OL,9,Fof that group."
OL,11,FMr Aguiar is running six world
OL,12,Fmarathon majors, an elite series of
OL,13,Fmarathons held across the globe, in
OL,14,Faid of Alice's WonderDance Foundation,
OL,15,Fwhich provides financial support to
OL,16,Fyoung dancers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
